{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/FileReader\"><code>FileReader()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>result</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort\"><code>abort()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\"><code>readAsArrayBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsBinaryString\"><code>readAsBinaryString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL\"><code>readAsDataURL()</code></a></li><li><em><code>readAsText()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort_event\"><code>abort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/load_event\"><code>load</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/progress_event\"><code>progress</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>File API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>readAsText()</code></strong> メソッドは、指定された <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> の内容を読み取るために使用します。読み取り操作が完了すると、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\" title=\"readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a> が <code>DONE</code> に変わり、 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadend (en-US)</a></code> イベントが発生し、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\" title=\"result\"><code>result</code></a> プロパティにはファイルの内容が文字列として格納されます。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>より新しい API が利用できます</strong><br>\n <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob/text\"><code>Blob.text()</code></a> メソッドは、ファイルをテキストとして読み取るための新しい Promise ベースの API です。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>instanceOfFileReader</var>.readAsText(<var>blob</var>[, <var>encoding</var>]);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"blob\"><code>blob</code></dt>\n <dd>メソッドで読み込む <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> オブジェクトです。</dd>\n <dt id=\"encoding\"><code>encoding</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">省略可</span></dt>\n <dd>読込の際に使用する文字エンコーディングを指定する文字列です。この引数が指定されなかった場合は UTF-8 で解釈されます。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#FileReader-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API<br><small lang=\"ja\">FileReader の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td>初回定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.FileReader.readAsText","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"あわせて参照","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"あわせて参照","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"readAsText() メソッドは、指定された Blob または File の内容を読み取るために使用します。読み取り操作が完了すると、 readyState が DONE に変わり、 loadend (en-US) イベントが発生し、 result プロパティにはファイルの内容が文字列として格納されます。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsText()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/filereader/readastext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/filereader/readastext/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader","title":"FileReader"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText","title":"FileReader.readAsText()"}],"pageTitle":"FileReader.readAsText() - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}